short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: An extension which adds additional features to the UofT Arts and Science Timetable.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: An extension for University of Toronto Arts and Science Students which adds functionality to the A&S Timetable. This includes fixing the scrolling bug on the timetable as well as live saving of timetable data to local storage.
